Instructions:

- Use JSON file along with find, filter, slice, to create API endpoints
- RESTful routes: plural term for data

Requirements:

- 3 routes
- 1 should return a collection (array)
- 1 should return a single result
- it should be RESTful

Stretch:

- Handle when single item data don't exist
- Accept filters via query params
- Build a frontend to show the data

Available endpoints
"/", API overview
"/horses", all horses
"/year/:year", horses born a specific year
"/horses/won", horses that have won competitions
"/horses/:horseId", specific book by ID
"search", with query - search for anything in books value
